    "SimplifiedChinese": "合金金属",
    "TencentChinese": "合金金属",
    "TraditionalChinese": "合金"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A popular metal alloy with a wide variety of uses. 'Dirty Bronze' has shed its scientific name in favor of the popular term for its color.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Pure Ferrite</span> and <span class=\"name name-earth\">Pyrite</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种常用的金属合金，具有多种用途。由于其颜色特点，“肮脏青铜”比它的学名更流行。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-earth\">纯铁氧体</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">黄铁矿</span>制作。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种常用的金属合金，具有多种用途。由于其颜色特点，“肮脏青铜”比它的学名更流行。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-earth\">纯铁氧体</span>和<span class=\"name name-earth\">黄铁矿</span>制作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "功能多樣的熱門金屬合金。由於其顏色，大多人皆不使用其學名，而直接稱其為「汙銅」。<br><br>可使用<span class=\"name name-earth\">純鐵氧體</span>與<span class=\"name name-earth\">黃鐵礦</span>製造。"
  },
